headline: M/A-Com (MTSI) Surges 13.0%: Is This an Indication of Further Gains?
summary: M/A-Com (MTSI) was a big mover last session on higher-than-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions might not help the stock continue moving higher in the near term.
